\par does in the course of this essay, how in the latter half of the
\par last century British Liberalism went over bodily to the philosophy
\par of Statism, and abjuring the political method of repealing
\par existent coercive measures, proceeded to outdo the
\par Tories in constructing new coercive measures of ever-increasing
\par particularity. This piece of British political history has
